00:33:06.276 --> 00:33:09.256 A:middle
room and I hear it loud and

00:33:09.256 --> 00:33:10.006 A:middle
clear.

00:33:10.496 --> 00:33:12.226 A:middle
But if a UI sound would be loud

00:33:12.226 --> 00:33:14.236 A:middle
like this it would become

00:33:14.386 --> 00:33:15.036 A:middle
unpleasant.

00:33:15.576 --> 00:33:18.276 A:middle
It only needs add this subtle

00:33:18.796 --> 00:33:19.596 A:middle
[inaudible] layer to the

00:33:19.596 --> 00:33:20.236 A:middle
interaction.

00:33:20.876 --> 00:33:22.486 A:middle
Now let's quickly reply to

00:33:22.486 --> 00:33:22.946 A:middle
Mitch.

